title: Visits and Tours to the Historic Center Lima and Miraflores
description: Lima is a city with a lot of history and a number of tourist attractions. You will enjoy with us this beautiful tour with our bilingual guide and our tourist transport to learn about the fascinating history and culture of the city of kings.
all_descriptions: Lima is a city with a lot of history and a number of tourist attractions. You will enjoy with us this beautiful tour with our bilingual guide and our tourist transport to learn about the fascinating history and culture of the city of kings.

ItineraryThis is a typical itinerary for this productStop At:El Parque del Amor, Malecon Cisneros 18, Lima PeruOur tour guide will show us the most romantic park in Lima, El Parque del Amor located on the Malecon Cisneros in Miraflores. This park has a beautiful panoramic view of the Pacific Ocean and a 12-meter-long sculpture depicted by two young lovers reclining kissing.Duration: 30 minutesStop At:Huaca Pucllana, Calle General Borgono s/n, cuadra 8, Lima 15074 PeruWe will visit panoramic the Huaca Pucllana; archaeological center belonging to the Lima culture, built by the pre-Incas who inhabited the city of Lima during the years 200 - 700 AD.Duration: 10 minutesPass By:Parque El Olivar de San Isidro, Av. Los Incas Delimited by Paz Soldán, La Republica and C. Ántero Aspíllaga Avenues, Lima 15073 PeruWe will visit El Olivar Park located in the district of San Isidro known for the lung of Lima since it has an extension of 87 km² and that has more than 1500 trees and 23 hectares of green areas.Stop At:Museo Central, Jr. Lampa 474, Lima 15001 PeruWe will visit the Central Reserve Bank of Peru where it preserves the monetary stability of the country, regulates the currency and credit, administrative.Duration: 1 hourStop At:Museo Convento San Francisco y Catacumbas, Jiron Ancash, Lima 15001 PeruWe will visit the San Francisco Church and Convent where we will visit inside beautiful paintings and paintings by famous artists; as well as its choir rooms, hall halls, penance room, chapter room, refectory room and more. We will enter below the crypt of the church to visit the catacombs museum where we will observe the crypts.Duration: 1 hourStop At:Plaza de Armas (Plaza Mayor), Jr. Junin and Jr. Carabaya, Lima PeruWe will tour the Plaza Mayor in Lima where the guide will tell us about its history and the founding of Lima. Around it we will observe the Government Palace of Peru, the Basilica Cathedral of Lima, the Archbishop's Palace, the Municipal Palace, the Club Union Building among others.Duration: 15 minutes
